<TITLE>Arts, Entertainment & Intellectual Property Law</TITLE>
</HEAD>

<BODY BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF" TEXT="#000000">

<CENTER>
<TABLE BORDER=2 CELLPADDING=0>
<TR>
