<TR>
</TABLE>
</CENTER>

<P>
<CENTER>
<TABLE BORDER=3 WIDTH=100%>
<TR>
<TH VALIGN=MIDDLE><A HREF="../lists/estwilltrustattys.html"><FONT SIZE=4>Leading Illinois Estate Planning, Wills &amp; Trusts Attorneys</FONT></TH>
</TR>
</TABLE>
</CENTER>

<P>
<CENTER>
<H1><STRONG>Estate Planning, Wills &amp; Trusts</STRONG></H1>
</CENTER>

<UL>
<LI><A HREF="#10">Estate Planning, Wills &amp; Trusts</A>
<UL>
<LI><A HREF="#20">Wills</A>
<UL>
<LI><A HREF="#30">Requirements for a Valid Will</A>
<LI><A HREF="#40">Personal Representative</A>
<LI><A HREF="#50">Appointing a Guardian for Children</A>
<LI><A HREF="#60">Planning for Incapacity</A>
