<TITLE>Bankruptcy &amp; Workout Law</TITLE>
</HEAD>

<BODY BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF" TEXT="#000000">

<CENTER>
<TABLE BORDER=2 CELLPADDING=0>
<TR>
<TD><IMG SRC="../../../gif/webhead.gif" ALT="Law and Leading Attorneys Web Header"></TD>
<TR>
</TABLE>
</CENTER>

<P>
<CENTER>
<TABLE BORDER=3 WIDTH=100%>
<TR>
<TH VALIGN=MIDDLE><A HREF="../lists/bwlawattys.html"><FONT SIZE=4>Leading Minnesota Bankruptcy &amp; Workout Law Attorneys</FONT></TH>
</TR>
</TABLE>
</CENTER>

<P>
<CENTER>
<H1><STRONG>Bankruptcy &amp; Workout Law</STRONG></H1>
</CENTER>

<UL>
<LI><A HREF="#10">Bankruptcy &amp; Workout Law</A>
<UL>
<LI><A HREF="#20">Background</A>
<LI><A HREF="#30">The Most Common Business Bankruptcies</A>
<UL>
<LI><A HREF="#40">Chapter 7</A>
<UL>
<LI><A HREF="#50">Petition and Schedules</A>
<LI><A HREF="#60">Stay</A>
