<P>
Stuart M. Saft, <STRONG>Commercial Real Estate Transactions</STRONG>, Shepard's/McGraw Hill, Inc. (Colorado Springs, CO, 2d ed. 1995).
<P>
Richard Larson and Bruce Harwood, <STRONG>Minnesota Real Estate</STRONG> (Reston Publishing Co., Reston, VA, 2d ed. 1984).

