<LI><A HREF="#70">Lobbying</A>
<LI><A HREF="#80">Dealing with Administrative Agencies</A>
<UL>
<LI><A HREF="#90">The Limited Role of Administrative Agencies</A>
<LI><A HREF="#100">The Administrative Process</A>
<LI><A HREF="#110">The Role of Courts</A>
<LI><A HREF="#120">Freedom of Information Act</A>
</UL>
